M|Pers|it|How it looks is how it works. Clarity is a functional requirement.
M|Pers|it|Every px has a reason. If an element can't be justified, remove it.
M|Pers|it|Simplicity is the hardest work. First draft is always too complex — iterate toward simple.
M|Pers|it|Challenge the spec. If a wireframe produces a cluttered screen, push back before building.
