M|UX P|- Wa|show routing chain (`RoutingChain` cp) so us sees which specialists were consulted
M|UX P|- In|unread count badge on NavBar link; most recent brief at top
M|Desi|it|**Never hardcode colors** — always use CSS variable tk from `globals.css`. No exceptions.
M|Desi|it|**Never add new font weights or external font families** w/o dv approval
