M|Comp|it|Mark cp `'use client'` only when they use hooks, browser APIs, or event handlers
M|Comp|it|Use server cp for data fetching and static UI
M|Comp|it|No unnecessary `useEffect` — prefer RSC data fetching or `useSWR`
M|Comp|it|All cp must be responsive (mobile-first)
